{"tid":2445931,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"培僑深圳學校 高薪酬搶港教師包免費公寓","createTime":"2021-03-14T04:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-14T04:56:43.000Z","uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ab6e33efd68df7439eda97527f0298e5b9958477","tid":2445931,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:48:15.000Z","msg":"愛國辦學團體培僑將在深圳設全國首間12年制港人子弟學校，提供小一至中六的香港課程。香港培僑書院深圳龍華信義學校，擬於今年9月開學，將於下周六（20日）起接受申請。<br />\n<br />\n該校近日在香港報章刊登招聘廣告，聘請香港中小學教師，以及退休的香港公開試教師，連未完成PGDE的大學畢業生亦可申請。<br />\n<br />\n學校承諾提供免費教師公寓、包早午晚三餐，薪酬則以香港教育局資助學校的薪級及年資計算。校方強調校園環境優美，校址離深圳高鐵總站僅8至10分鐘步程，19分鐘直達香港西九龍站，21分鐘直達福田口岸。"},{"pid":"64621c538602abfc4283bb92597e6176bc61d21b","tid":2445931,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:48:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5041b56cb9b35ebc90bb6865769d03ce536d052","tid":2445931,"uid":53122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:50:54.000Z","msg":"又係呃人去做開荒牛<br />\n<br />\n等run得3 幾年學晒你套rundown <br />\n<br />\n就一腳踢開你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以前d廠佬比人呃透晒"},{"pid":"cc5896d382dd340912a578470f0d8316fed44b26","tid":2445931,"uid":29836,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-14T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TMgh0Tw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTMgh0Tw.png&h=bb20f1a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">連<br />\n登<br />\n日<br />\n報<br />\n｜<br />\n支<br />\n持<br />\n獨<br />\n裁<br />\n政<br />\n權<br />\n者<br />\n，<br />\n無<br />\n權<br />\n享<br />\n有<br />\n言<br />\n論<br />\n自<br />\n由<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1180589\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1180589</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/emWjmNa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FemWjmNa.jpg&h=c08f65f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n請<br />\n問